story :
This mixed-blood girl from a footballer father who comes from Catalan and mother from Indramayu dreams of becoming a dancer, but her mother prefers Sophia to be a mentalist. In order not to hurt his mother's heart he studied dance and magic at the same time. Unknowingly, Sophia is so immersed in both and has an edge in dance that can hypnotize people even evil who see her do what she tells her to do.
